// Code-signing team for the MyPortrait Xcode target.
//
// The default below is the upstream maintainer's Apple Developer team. It lets
// the maintainer run `xcodegen generate` and build without any extra setup.
//
// Contributors (anyone not in team VYHNX2Y2AL) must override it with their own
// Apple ID's team — otherwise Xcode falls back to ad-hoc "Sign to Run Locally",
// whose designated requirement contains a `cdhash` that changes on every
// rebuild, which makes TCC silently revoke screen-recording / mic permission
// every time you build.
//
// To override: create `Support/Signing.local.xcconfig` (gitignored) with:
//     DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = YOURTEAMID
// then re-run `xcodegen generate`. The #include? below is "optional include"
// (Xcode 11+ syntax) — missing file is fine, present file wins.

DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = VYHNX2Y2AL

#include? "Signing.local.xcconfig"
